title: Good Omens 1x4 REACTION!! "Saturday Morning Funtime"
author: Blind Wave
comment: Watch next week's Reaction to Good Omens 1x5 "The Doomsday Option"  Early HERE: https://www.patreon.com/posts/36828545

“We’ve got David Tennant here, we’ll be okay”
I often use this philosophy in life too
I like how Calvin's image is stuck in a meme-able expression for the rest of the vid
The book specifies that Pestilence had retired in 1936 while "muttering about penicillin".
So many people gloss over the Gavotte bit as an irrelevant tangent, but I love how much it tells you about Aziraphale's character in such a quick burst of narration.
description: Eric Rick Calvin and Aaron react to and discuss season 1 episode 4 of Good Omens - Saturday Morning Funtime - #GoodOmens
